Use the standard library

This is how to get_max_triples of n:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that a is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that b is 0
      Do this n times:
         Remember that c is 0
         Do this n times:
            When sum of a and b and c is n, then:
               When a is at most b, then:
                  When b is at most c, then:
                     Increase count
                  End when
               End when
            End when
            Increase c
         End do
         Increase b
      End do
      Increase a
   End do
   The answer is count
Now you know